"Rather than cognitive factors, the social structure of a species (e.g. how long juveniles spend in close proximity to their parents), and demographic variables (e.g. the size of social groups and their spatial distribution) have a major influence on the probability that Culture2 and Culture3 will emerge." (Heyes 2020:10)},
